Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.50,0:01:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治5年9月\N新桥和横滨间的铁路开通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.27,0:01:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连接世界船只群集的\N横滨和日本首都东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所需时间不超过1个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.85,0:01:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从英国引进的蒸气火车头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.12,0:02:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可牵引八节车厢以\N时速40公里的速度前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正可说是文明开化的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.23,0:02:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其利用者乃是以\N经营国外贸易的商人为主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在当时 因为传言火车头\N所发出的火会引起火灾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 铁道大部份\N都被设计在海岸边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.51,0:02:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也因此 天晴时可以看到\N远方的下总群山和富士山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.75,0:02:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二话\N第一次的蒸气火车仰天大事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.24,0:02:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火车进站了 不快点会来不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.94,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出门了还在磨蹭的是谁啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有备无患呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是应有的观念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！我可不是自愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.66,0:03:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为你每天在道场工作很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.76,0:03:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也该让你散散心\N才让你坐坐蒸气火车呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还得谢谢我呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了 两个别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个够了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光吵嘴也无济于事 对吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了就开心地玩吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 这么多人聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.59,0:03:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是来看火车\N不该会这么多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包了一整车厢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面装的好像是以前的金币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.37,0:04:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是现在英国的贸易商人\N正在上特别车厢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.61,0:04:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然漂亮蒸气火车真是华丽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豁出去花这钱是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.61,0:04:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔大玩一下也是需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了横滨一定要去吃\N西洋的甜点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种叫秀可拉多的甜点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后大家一起照照相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 还有 要看看洋装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.40,0:04:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱 更纱 真好听的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了 谁是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 无忧无虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以说师傅无忧无虑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火车就要开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请送行的人下车等待发车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有意见的话\N现在下车也可以哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.15,0:05:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁买给你的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.22,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊！很贵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这票一张要花一块钱耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.70,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要感谢我的慷慨大方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下车！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要下车！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要下车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 把左之助拦住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是被狐狸给迷惑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一醒 人已在粪坑里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.67,0:06:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.91,0:06:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不照相\N那东西会吸取人的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还相信那种事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我问你为什么\N这么大的东西会动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.52,0:06:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了嘛\N是蒸气的动力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒸气不是就开水的蒸气吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.29,0:06:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴啊 水壶的蒸气怎么\N推动这么重的东西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是白痴啊\N火车头哪里是水壶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你好好地说明看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.10,0:06:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为…名叫史迪文生的人\N他烧开水时发现壶盖被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看火车头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看看驾驶室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘客要乖乖地坐着别捣蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小气！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是车掌 不得了了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.91,0:07:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 马上把火车停住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出事了 必须马上停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停车？是什么大事啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸精和水壶\N是哪一个说不通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是水壶！是狐狸精！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说水壶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么嘴硬就叫剑心来评评理吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 在下也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别座的客人说 马上停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.09,0:08:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点奇怪 你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 回话啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你停车…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.31,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是假的\N一定有什么阴谋 不能停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.88,0:09:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子！\N果然刚才应该把你丢出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.14,0:09:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快停车\N否则把这小鬼丢下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是金币！一定是想抢金币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴！把嘴巴闭起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一名乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,途中若是被你停住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.46,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期待的横滨观光就去不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.09,0:10:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想把连结器打开是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你不像是普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.11,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真累 这梯子真累人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.28,0:11:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 做生意 当强盗\N都很难随心所欲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.82,0:11:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要…请你退场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.56,0:12:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰！不准碰你的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真难对付\N不过到此为止了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.76,0:12:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住！小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管他 没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.15,0:13:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到达预定地之前\N把特别车厢切离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.84,0:13:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真久 祢彦和剑心在磨蹭什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.64,0:13:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如我所说 他们两个现在醒了\N正在粪坑里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真固执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了 剑心他….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心他….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连结器打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来就是等待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板 大庭广众之下\N搬给人家看是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警卫的人数都被知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托人家来抢是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  车速还没慢下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.57,0:14:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这叫作人算不如天算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 开我玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.21,0:14:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多危险啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你躲一边看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.69,0:14:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑\N我可是神谷活心流代理师傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大意失荆州喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我只是个小孩子\N身体轻可是足以自傲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死心吧 来呀 来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我们坐同一辆车\N可是你的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别高兴的太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是海盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.04,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多船啊….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你们捣蛋 计划有些乱\N不过 也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.89,0:16:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把金币运完之前\N你们就在这乖乖等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫你不准动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.87,0:16:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我多费手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地不乱来 我不会动粗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.41,0:16:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是绅士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜欢看到血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算追上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.14,0:17:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 到这地步 万事已迟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想干嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋 你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.90,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…放手小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 乖乖地离开这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑 伙计们干掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快离开这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.79,0:18:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助和薰小姐弄连接器\N祢彦麻烦你去帮机关手的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋 看你们打算\N怎样从这里逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻碍全部清除干净为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流…龙槌闪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.69,0:19:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能追的快追 别让火车逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.71,0:19:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是蒸气火车 船可追不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.35,0:19:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底是谁….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 真是太好了 剑心….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰小姐很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 惹人厌的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在那儿抱着腿发抖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.12,0:20:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说无论如何都要我们收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.96,0:20:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢你 多亏你的相救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.73,0:20:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么用 就让薰小姐作主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这么多的钱….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要的话 我拿喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.14,0:20:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.47,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要不要照相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要 灵魂会被吸掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在说 那是迷信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要说几次才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.19,0:20:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 每拍一张寿命就缩短一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是恶魔的机器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.79,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你们两个别再吵嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.76,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 摆那什么姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 照片就拍不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么嘛 一点也没影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.21,0:21:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拍喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.94,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 我要拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.48,0:21:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要拉我的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个好了没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要…
